Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:09.45,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,Nee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:27.14,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,So cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:31.53,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:43.11,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}Step 1, restrain me in a coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:46.03,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}Step 2, bury me under a gravestone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.56,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}Step 3, start a three count.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:53.13,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's as far as this domain's guaranteed-hit effect applies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:55.29,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is a special-grade disease curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:59.89,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't break out of the coffin before the count is up,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:03.50,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll contract that disease and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:19.14,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real issue is that gravestone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:23.71,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I eat that attack twice more, I'll no longer be able to move, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:27.21,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wouldn't want to fight Geto{**-kun} in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:29.83,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Ui Ui, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.25,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,Yes, Nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:38.60,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's probably reflexively targeting the person with
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:40.92,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,the strongest cursed energy in its domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:46.37,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Only two crows were sucked into the domain with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.40,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:07.61,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}So in order to take it down,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.88,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to shift its target to Ui Ui
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:14.27,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}so he can buy me time to operate freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:19.77,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Ui Ui will die after taking one hit from that gravestone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.50,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Ui Ui...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:27.90,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Will you die for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:35.21,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's all right? May I die for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:57.38,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}The moment I released my cursed energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:59.47,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nee-sama suppressed hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.09,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand everything now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.33,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:28.12,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Did you think I only brought that boy to carry my things?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.87,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nee-sama's request that I risk my life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:36.15,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}is the signal permitting me to use my cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:40.26,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Ui Ui's role is dealing with domains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:44.35,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It goes against my principles to owe anyone anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:47.13,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,So I leave that aspect up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:32.70,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What do you think is the greatest way to instantly boost a sorcerer's base power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:36.15,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,It's using a pact that puts your life on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.73,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,Right, Nee-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.65,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:43.90,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}The crowning attack of Nee-sama's cursed technique, Black Bird Manipulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.52,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}is Kamikaze: Bird Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:49.64,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}She forces her crow to commit suicide, which in return
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.24,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}removes the limit on a crow's normally feeble cursed energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.04,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}as she makes them slam into her opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:57.77,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}No human is able to stop her Bird Strike,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.74,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,{\i1}with the sole exception of Gojo Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:11.89,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone, it's the main event.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:17.13,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Will you die for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.73,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.98,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,For a modern sorcerer.
Comment: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:26.01,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:56.02,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:59.54,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Gojo Satoru has been sealed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.75,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,I feel like I've been bushwhacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:03.46,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:07.59,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Geto{**-san} is involved, though, even if he is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:10.22,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I imagine the trick lies there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:16.76,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,I'd be happy to toast the fall of the Gojo clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:21.13,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Go home if you're not going to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:23.66,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Go home, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:26.82,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,That's what you should be doing, Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:30.15,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Right, grade 1 sorcerer, Nanami-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.54,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Maki{**-san},
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.44,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,you should do what he says in this regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:37.91,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I'll be far more useful than some drunkard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.33,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,{\an8}Have you been drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:42.46,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, I hafn'h been dwinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:49.02,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess there's never been a case where I was better off alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:01.57,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Nanami{**-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:02.81,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:11.82,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I'll take this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:27.13,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,You guys are a bit too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:37.42,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:38.72,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.72,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}It must be his technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:02.87,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,How many people have you eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.52,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,Jogo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:17.08,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,Mahito...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:20.22,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,Hanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:26.99,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,Hanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:30.70,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,How dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.69,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,How dare you kill Hanami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:36.10,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,...kill Hanami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:40.78,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,I see. No wonder you were weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:45.87,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,You were still only a Curse Womb, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.46,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.86,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,And such a vast amount of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.78,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Cursed spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:20.20,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,do you know how many frames there are in one second of animation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.03,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,It's not "cursed spirit." I am Dagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:27.80,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,There's a modern tendency to raise resolutions and frame rates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:31.62,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,There's Hanami, Jogo, and Mahito, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:37.11,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Upscaling to 4K, and 60fps frame interpolation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.63,Default,Dago,0,0,0,,We all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:43.23,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,They don't cause anyone any trouble when done for personal use, so that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:49.27,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,However, modern TVs have their damn frame interpolation set to "on" by default!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:54.30,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,It's not like "unwanted favor" has become a dead phrase already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.92,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Nothing is more lamentable than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.48,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Creating that soap opera effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:01.03,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,We all have names!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:04.61,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Don't you agree that's uncultured?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.10,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Whoa there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:42.42,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}No damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:46.47,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or rather, it feels more like he has endless HP.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:02.30,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,I can't believe two grade 1s like us couldn't exorcise it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.89,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,What dire straits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.01,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:08.53,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the old man hadn't used his technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.81,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would have died there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.14,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:15.65,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,A defensive barrier of water, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:18.66,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Can you produce large-scale attacks at the same time, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.14,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,You have too much cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:22.90,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,You still have several techniques left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.92,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,So what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:27.74,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.74,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,I'll kill you quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.75,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,before you can use your technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.84,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:49.97,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Of course, you can hover, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.58,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,I'd escape upward, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:58.81,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't activate my technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:08.20,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.22,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's this man's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.99,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:24.41,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}Probably faster than Jogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Projection Sorcery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:35.88,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The cursed technique of Naobito Zenin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:40.56,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,It splits one second into 24 frames from his field of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:45.27,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,and allows him to trace the actions created in those frames at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:46.94,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,While the technique is active,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.56,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,anyone Naobito touches with his hand must also
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:53.87,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,define their actions within 1/24th of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.53,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,If they fail to do so, then their action hangs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:59.19,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,and they remain frozen for one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.71,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,There are risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:08.16,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The actions defined cannot be edited halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:12.14,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Creating actions that excessively ignore physics and paths of motion
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:15.27,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,will result in him freezing, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:30.85,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Still, with his innate sense for frame beats and time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:36.73,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,he's managed to become the fastest sorcerer, aside from Gojo Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.66,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,I won't let you.
Comment: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:08.01,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.33,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,Domain Expansion:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.63,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,Horizon of the Captivating Skandha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:35.54,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shikigami?! So this is the domain's guaranteed-hit attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:37.14,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't notice them until they struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:40.79,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, they didn't even exist until they hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.81,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Secret Art: Falling Blossom Emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,An anti-domain technique passed down among the big three clans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:52.82,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Like Simple Domain, the user does not activate their own domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:55.99,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,and instead, the moment the domain's guaranteed-hit attack activates,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:59.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,it protects the user by countering with their own cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:02.80,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew that man was different from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:04.66,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm done testing their strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:09.56,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll split my power, 70% to the mustached man, and 30% to the man in a suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:13.88,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,Activate technique: Death Swarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.66,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Maki{**-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:23.35,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,The shikigami aren't heading straight for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:27.36,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,They'll be gouging out our flesh in the next instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.79,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Don't think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:32.57,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,The moment you feel contact, cut them down one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:35.74,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,That's the best you can manage with your scant cursed en—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:40.14,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Nanami{**-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:52.18,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,{\i1}The surge of shikigami isn't abating at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:55.59,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it possible the technique embedded into this domain is—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:05.69,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,Falling—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:10.94,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,The sea is the source of all life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.74,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,Weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:17.74,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,You're first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:26.16,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,Death Swarm is a swarm of endlessly emerging shikigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:36.88,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,If you're gonna call me weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.31,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,then kill me in a single blow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.02,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Octobitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:46.39,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,Then I'll devour you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:47.92,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.61,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,...just like the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.48,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Maki{**-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.29,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:08.46,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,{\i1}You really are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:13.21,Default,Maki,0,0,0,,{\i1}one hell of a cheeky underclassman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.12,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.26,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,{\i1}That octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.13,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's the source of this domain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:23.89,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}You dare infiltrate my domain on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.14,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.29,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:49.86,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}The guaranteed-hit effect of my domain is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:54.46,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}That boy is deploying his domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:58.81,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, his domain and mine are playing tug-of-war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:01.41,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to regain my guaranteed-hit effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:05.10,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to crush his domain first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.65,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,Easily done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:29.82,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,The other two?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:31.80,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Ino{**-san} tapped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.50,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Itadori's acting on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:36.10,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:38.63,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Please focus on your domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:43.00,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:47.08,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}He endured Death Swarm for roughly a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:50.02,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}The mustachioed man, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:06.44,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,You only took one measly right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:11.08,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,But it had 71 years in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.09,Default,Naobito,0,0,0,,That's going to cost you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:23.80,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this state keeps up, we have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.50,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,{\i1\i0}If{\i1} it keeps up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.33,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Nanami{**-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:40.37,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,That octopus currently thinks our domains are pushing for control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:42.53,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,But my goal is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:47.06,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I'll open a small hole
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:49.22,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,in the barrier of this domain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:52.90,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,The hole I entered through is already sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:54.94,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,It's harder to open one from inside than outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:59.63,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,but I can open a hole large enough for someone to pass through for a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.78,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,That thing isn't Gojo{*}{*-sensei}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:05.53,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be able to use Domain Expansion multiple times in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:08.64,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Once we're all out of this domain, we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:10.71,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,The edge of his domain is beneath my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:13.04,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I can tell, since I touched it when I entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.30,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I'm ready to go at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:16.54,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,If all three of you jump in once...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:21.00,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,None of this leaving yourself behind alone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.31,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I'm risking my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.30,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,but I don't intend to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:30.34,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:33.00,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Gather 'round!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:42.26,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're bolstering their defense of the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:44.21,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}That just groups them up for me to—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.34,Default,Dagon,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:49.66,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}He figured it out?! But it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.97,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,To Fushiguro{**-kun}'s feet!
Comment: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:10.06,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:40.07,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.28,0:23:43.75,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Don't you think sibling relationships tend to show through in a person's character?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:45.74,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,Nee-sama, that could encourage the discriminatory
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:47.28,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,idea that all only children are selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:48.44,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,You're right, that's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:49.68,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,Are you refuting Nee-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:50.28,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:51.72,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Next time, "Fluctuations, Part 2."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:53.04,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,What about Gojo Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:54.76,Default,Both,0,0,0,,He's an only child, of course.
